---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Timekeeping Solutions — Pink Payroll" description="Accurate employee time tracking integrated directly with your payroll. Eliminate buddy punching, reduce manual errors, and sync seamlessly with iSolved timekeeping.">

  <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-5">Timekeeping Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6 max-w-3xl">
        Stop "Time Theft" and<br class="hidden md:block" />
        <span class="text-pink">Reclaim Your Profitability.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Manual timesheets aren't just a headache — they are a leak in your cash flow. If you aren't tracking time digitally, you are likely paying for labor that never happened.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CASE STUDIES ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Numbers Don't Lie</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">📉 The Real Cost of "Wasted Minutes"</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Small errors add up to massive annual losses. Consider these two common scenarios:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

      <!-- Case #1 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Case #1</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black">The 4-Minute Leak</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
          Just 15 employees receiving pay for merely <strong class="text-brand-black">4 minutes of "wasted" time</strong> per day — untracked breaks, extended lunches, or rounded punch times — totals <strong class="text-brand-black">23 hours of additional pay</strong> per month.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto bg-pink/5 border border-pink/20 rounded-xl px-5 py-4">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-pink mb-1">The Cost</p>
          <p class="text-brand-black font-semibold text-sm leading-relaxed">
            At an average pay rate of $20.00/hr, you are losing <strong>$460.00 every single month</strong> to the "void."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Case #2 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Case #2</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black">The Admin Burden</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
          The average payroll clerk spends <strong class="text-brand-black">7 minutes per time card</strong> verifying totals and reconstructing lost data. Preparing just 25 manual time cards takes nearly <strong class="text-brand-black">3 hours per pay period.</strong>
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto bg-pink/5 border border-pink/20 rounded-xl px-5 py-4">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-pink mb-1">The Cost</p>
          <p class="text-brand-black font-semibold text-sm leading-relaxed">
            At a $25.00/hr clerical wage, you're spending over <strong>$150.00 a month</strong> just on the "act" of counting hours.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== SECURE DIGITAL TIMEKEEPING ===== -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light-gray/40 border-y border-brand-light-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Platform</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">🧬 Secure Digital Timekeeping</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We utilize the iSolved© platform to bring your timekeeping into the 21st century. No software to buy or install — just secure, cloud-based precision.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <!-- Digital & Mobile -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="text-4xl">🤳</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-1">Digital & Mobile</h3>
            <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">The Virtual Clock</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
            Employees can simply pin our secure browser-based portal to their home screen for instant access. Includes <strong class="text-brand-black">Geofencing</strong> to ensure staff are actually on-site when they clock in.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Biometric & Physical -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <div class="text-4xl">🧬</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-1">Biometric & Physical</h3>
            <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">The Wall Clock</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed mb-2">The ultimate defense against "buddy punching."</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-pink flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </span>
              <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-brand-black">Biometric (Fingerprint/Face):</strong> Verification through unique biological traits ensures the right person is on the clock.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-pink flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
              </span>
              <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <strong class="text-brand-black">Proximity & Key Code:</strong> Use standard key cards, fobs, or custom PINs for high-speed entry.
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== SEAMLESS IMPORTS ===== -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-start max-w-3xl">
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-5xl">🔌</div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="text-pink text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Bring Your Own Tech</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-black mb-4">Seamless Software Imports</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Already love your current system? No problem. We can create custom imports for the industry's most popular tools:
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-brand-black font-extrabold text-sm mb-2">🍽️ Restaurants</p>
            <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Toast, Aloha, Clover</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-brand-light-gray rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-brand-black font-extrabold text-sm mb-2">🛍️ Retail & Service</p>
            <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Homebase, Deputy, QuickBooks Time</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== BENEFITS TABLE + CTA ===== -->
  <section class="bg-pink text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2">📊 Benefits at a Glance</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b-2 border-white/30">
              <th class="text-left py-4 pr-6 text-pink-light font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-xs w-2/5">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-left py-4 text-pink-light font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-xs">Benefit to You</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-white/20">
            {[
              { feature: 'Integrated Payroll', benefit: 'Time flows directly to paychecks — zero manual entry.' },
              { feature: 'Real-Time Alerts',   benefit: 'Get notified of missed breaks or unauthorized overtime.' },
              { feature: 'CA Compliance',      benefit: 'Automated tracking for mandated lunch and rest breaks.' },
            ].map(({ feature, benefit }) => (
              <tr>
                <td class="py-4 pr-6 font-bold text-white">{feature}</td>
                <td class="py-4 text-pink-light leading-relaxed">{benefit}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-pink font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-base"
        >
          Request a Timekeeping Demo
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
